quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  22,56,"Gbogbo ìjọba ọjọ́ yẹn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu tí Ó máa ṣèdájọ́ láààrin wọn. Nítorí náà, àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere, (wọn yóò wà) nínú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra.",""
  22,57,"Àwọn tó sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́, tí wọ́n tún pe àwọn āyah Wa ní irọ́; àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni ìyà tí í yẹpẹrẹ ẹ̀dá sì wà fún.",""
  22,58,"Àwọn tí wọ́n gbé ìlú wọn jù sílẹ̀ nítorí ẹ̀sìn Allāhu, lẹ́yìn náà, tí wọ́n pa wọ́n tàbí tí wọ́n kú; dájúdájú Allāhu yóò pèsè fún wọn ní ìpèsè tó dára. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Ó mà l’óore jùlọ nínú àwọn olùpèsè.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah as-Sọ̄ffāt; 37:125."
  22,59,"Dájúdájú (Allāhu) yóò fi wọ́n sínú àyè kan tí wọn yóò yọ́nú sí. Dájúdájú Allāhu mà ni Onímọ̀, Aláfaradà.",""
  22,60,"Ìyẹn (nìyẹn). Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì gbẹ̀san irú ìyà tí wọ́n fi jẹ ẹ́, lẹ́yìn náà tí wọ́n bá tún ṣàbòsí sí i, dájúdájú Allāhu yóò ṣàrànṣe fún un. Dájúdájú Allāhu mà ni Alámòjúúkúrò, Aláforíjìn.",""
  22,61,"Ìyẹn nítorí pé dájúdájú Allāhu ń fi òru bọ inú ọ̀sán, Ó sì ń fi ọ̀sán bọ inú òru. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Olùgbọ́, Olùríran.",""
  22,62,"Ìyẹn nítorí pé dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Òdodo. Àti pé dájúdájú ohun tí wọ́n ń pè lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀ ni irọ́. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Ó ga, Ó tóbi.",""
  22,63,"Ṣé o ò rí i pé dájúdájú Allāhu ń sọ omi kalẹ̀ láti sánmọ̀, ilẹ̀ sì máa lọ́ràá wá? Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Aláàánú, Alámọ̀tán.",""
  22,64,"TiRẹ̀ ni ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun mà ni Ọlọ́rọ̀, Ẹlẹ́yìn.",""
